  "base_path": "/transfer-driving-instructor-registration-gb",
  "content_id": "4d651659-b6c1-4d1b-8a93-2f398060e858",
  "description": "Transfer your Northern Ireland or European Union (EU) driving instructor registration to Great Britain.",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>Apply to transfer your Northern Ireland or European Union (<abbr title=\"European Union\">EU</abbr>) driving instructor registration to Great Britain. It costs £300.</p>\n\n<p>This service is available from 6am to 11:30pm.</p>\n\n",
    "more_information": "<p><a href=\"/criminal-record-check-become-driving-instructor\">Get a criminal record disclosure number</a> if you’ve lived in Great Britain for at least 12 months. You cannot use one you have already - you must get a new one.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>If you’ve lived in Great Britain for less than 12 months, <a href=\"/government/publications/criminal-records-checks-for-overseas-applicants\">get a ‘certificate of good character’</a> from the country you were living in before. You need a translation in English.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-happens-next\">What happens next</h2>\n\n<p>You’ll need to send documents to the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (<abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr>) to finish your application. <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr> will contact you and tell you what to send.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"help-with-your-application\">Help with your application</h2>\n\n<p>Email <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr> to get help applying online.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>DVSA</strong>\\<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:customerservices@dvsa.gov.uk\">customerservices@dvsa.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There’s a different service to <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nidirect.gov.uk/services/apply-become-adi-or-ami-online\">transfer a Great Britain or EU registration to Northern Ireland</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
    "transaction_start_link": "https://driver-services.dvsa.gov.uk/irdta",
    "variants": [

    ],
    "will_continue_on": "the Department for Transport website"
  },
